description:
Are you ready to explore the Three Angels’ Messages from a new perspective? 

In this inspiring YouTube video, Willie and Elaine Oliver of Family Ministries share how the Three Angels’ Messages can be viewed through a family lens. They share the connection between the Three Angels' Messages and the family by returning to the Old Testament and referencing the Book of Malachi. The passage they discuss is Malachi 4:5-6, which talks about the coming of Elijah the Prophet before the great and terrible day of the Lord. Elijah's mission is to turn the hearts of the fathers back to their children and the children's hearts to their fathers so that the land will not be destroyed.

As they explore this passage, Willie and Elaine highlight how it reveals God's plan for families at the end of time. They discuss the Three Angels' Messages in more detail, emphasizing the importance of worshiping God and not giving in to the world's temptations. They also discuss the concept of Babylon and how it relates to our modern-day society.

Let us get involved in the primary mission of the Church and prioritize our families as we prepare for the end of time. If you're ready to explore the Three Angels' messages in a new light, this video is a must-watch. 

The Seventh-day Adventist Church has been an established denomination since 1863. It is a global Christian family with over 21 million members who hold the Bible as the ultimate authority. We are believers who promise to help people understand the Bible to find freedom, healing, and hope in Jesus.
